                                </svg>
                                <span class="ms-2 fs-6 flex-grow-1">Continue with Google</span>
                            </a>
                            <a href="#!" class="btn bsb-btn-2xl btn-outline-dark rounded-0 d-flex align-items-center">
                                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-apple text-dark" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                                    <path d="M11.182.008C11.148-.03 9.923.023 8.857 1.18c-1.066 1.156-.902 2.482-.878 2.516.024.034 1.520.087 2.475-1.258.955-1.345.762-2.391.728-2.43Zm3.314 11.733c-.048-.096-2.325-1.234-2.113-3.422.212-2.189 1.675-2.789 1.698-2.854.023-.065-.597-.79-1.254-1.157a3.692 3.692 0 0 0-1.563-.434c-.108-.003-.483-.095-1.254.116-.508.139-1.653.589-1.968.607-.316.018-1.256-.522-2.267-.665-.647-.125-1.333.131-1.824.328-.49.196-1.422.754-2.074 2.237-.652 1.482-.311 3.83-.067 4.56.244.729.625 1.924 1.273 2.796.576.984 1.34 1.667 1.659 1.899.319.232 1.219.386 1.843.067.502-.308 1.408-.485 1.766-.472.357.013 1.276.086 1.767-.271.49-.358 1.149-1.544.862-2.434Z" />
                                </svg>
                                <span class="ms-2 fs-6 flex-grow-1">Continue with Apple</span>
                            </a>
                            <a href="#!" class="btn bsb-btn-2xl btn-outline-dark rounded-0 d-flex align-items-center">
                                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-facebook text-primary" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                                    <path d="M6.598 0C2.967 0 0 3.134 0 6.99c0 2.724 1.672 5.067 4.027 6.197v3.59h2.24v-4.03h-2.24v-3.079c0-2.213 1.354-3.418 3.401-3.418 1.376 0 2.623.128 2.95.128v2.69h-2.018c-1.046 0-1.373.682-1.373 1.372v2.364h2.44l-.417 2.74h-2.023V16c2.253-.847 3.973-3.396 3.973-6.99C12.196 3.134 9.229 0 6.598 0z" />
                                </svg>
                                <span class="ms-2 fs-6 flex-grow-1">Continue with Facebook</span>
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

